description.en:
We are a Japanese music production company. We mainly provide music for idols and videos for YouTubers. Deployment of self-developed SNS-type NFT marketplace application.
In the app, we convert our works into NFT and sell them. It will be developed as a token that can be used within the app.
Once the app becomes popular, we will develop our own platform so that it can be used more in the field of NFT.
